<title>mạttdẖmrsẖ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mạttdẖmrsẖ ʿly̱ ạlḥạlẗ wʿ
 ạlṣḥẗ ạlly ạ̹nt fyhạ
 mạttdẖmrsẖ dy yạmạ nạs wsṭ ạlmrḍ msẖ btlạqyhạ
 ạlqrạr- ạrfʿ ʿynyk lfwq qwl lh yạrb ạ̉sẖkrk
